review_blob: This is my favorite beer right now. Pretty much compare everything I drink to it. Citrusy and smooth no harsh bitterness.
Was very enjoyable. Distinct taste had me rolling it around my tongue before the swallow

Tasted a bit medicinal and there was much too much head after the beer was poured and it didnt go down much after pouring. Wish it was served in 16.9 oz cans 

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone
